Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:29.44,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}在這便利至上的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:34.70,ED_CH,,700,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}滿屏的廣告與惡意  一指便能輕鬆解決
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:38.45,ED_CH,,1000,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}可在你面前  我卻亂了節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.45,0:22:41.25,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}變得像瘋掉的人偶一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:42.71,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}你還真是神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.71,0:22:51.68,ED_CH,,0,1000,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}我的偽裝如春雪融化般漸漸褪去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:57.35,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}伴隨傾心愛慕而生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:23:01.77,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}這份酸甜與苦澀讓我束手無策
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:03.60,ED_CH,,0,1000,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}想逃離現代生活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:05.73,ED_CH,,0,1000,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}將一切都毀掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.73,0:23:11.07,ED_CH,,0,700,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}侵蝕心底的病毒  根本找不到解法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:13.36,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}疼痛啊  疼痛啊  都飛走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.36,0:23:15.70,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}1.2.3  敲擊漏電
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:17.70,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}麻痺刺痛  不停震顫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.08,0:23:21.66,ED_CH,,0,800,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}想逃離現代生活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.66,0:23:23.92,ED_CH,,0,800,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}每次觸碰都改變的算法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:29.09,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}將「那是擬人化」的詭辯揉成紙團丟掉  來跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:30.80,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}別按下UNDO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:33.68,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}哪怕這是本世紀最大錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:38.81,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}LYLA...第一次呼吸
